# Prismatic · Environment Variables Reference

## Required

### LLM Provider
```
# Choose provider: deepseek (default, cost-effective), openai, or anthropic
LLM_PROVIDER=deepseek

# DeepSeek API (recommended — $0.14/1M tokens input)
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-key

# OR OpenAI API
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-key

# OR Anthropic API
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key
```

## Required: Database

Prismatic uses Prisma with PostgreSQL, MySQL, or SQLite.

```
# PostgreSQL (recommended for production)
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:5432/prismatic?schema=public"

# MySQL
# DATABASE_URL="mysql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:3306/prismatic"

# SQLite (dev only)
# DATABASE_URL="file:./dev.db"
```

## Required: Authentication (NextAuth.js)

```
# Generate with `openssl rand -base64 32`
AUTH_SECRET=your-secret-key-here

# NextAuth URL (defaults to production URL in production)
NEXTAUTH_URL=https://prismatic.zxqconsulting.com
```

### Email Registration & Login (SMTP)
```
# SMTP Configuration (pick one provider below)

# Option A: Resend (recommended — https://resend.com)
RESEND_API_KEY=re_your_key
EMAIL_FROM=Prismatic <noreply@prismatic.app>

# Option B: SendGrid
# SENDGRID_API_KEY=SG.your_key
# EMAIL_FROM=noreply@prismatic.app

# Option C: SMTP (Gmail, custom SMTP, etc.)
# EMAIL_SERVER_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# EMAIL_SERVER_PORT=587
# EMAIL_SERVER_USER=your@email.com
# EMAIL_SERVER_PASSWORD=your_app_password
# EMAIL_FROM=Prismatic <noreply@prismatic.app>
```

### SMS Verification (Phone Login)
```
# Option A: 阿里云短信 (中国大陆)
# ALIYUN_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_access_key_id
# ALIYUN_ACCESS_KEY_SECRET=your_access_key_secret
# ALIYUN_SMS_SIGN_NAME=Prismatic
# ALIYUN_SMS_TEMPLATE_CODE=SMS_xxxxxxx

# Option B: Twilio (international)
# TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your_account_sid
# TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_auth_token
# TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+1234567890
```

### WeChat OAuth
```
# Register at: https://open.weixin.qq.com → 网站应用 → 申请注册
# Wait for approval (1-7 days), then get AppID and AppSecret from app details
WECHAT_APP_ID=your_wechat_app_id
WECHAT_APP_SECRET=your_wechat_app_secret
```

### OAuth: GitHub
```
# Create OAuth App at: https://github.com/settings/developers
AUTH_GITHUB_ID=your-github-client-id
AUTH_GITHUB_SECRET=your-github-client-secret
```

### OAuth: Google
```
# Create OAuth App at: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
AUTH_GOOGLE_ID=your-google-client-id
AUTH_GOOGLE_SECRET=your-google-client-secret
```

## Optional

### Demo Accounts (Development Only)
```
# Format: email1:password1,email2:password2,...
# Leave empty or unset to disable demo accounts in production
DEMO_ACCOUNTS=demo1@prismatic.app:DemoPass1!,demo2@prismatic.app:DemoPass2!
```

### Security
```
# Admin bypass for demo users (NEVER set to true in production)
# Defaults to false — always requires DB role check in production
ALLOW_ADMIN_BYPASS=false

# Application version (for health check reporting)
APP_VERSION=1.0.0
```

### Analytics
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=phc_your_key
```

### Storage
```
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=
S3_BUCKET=prismatic-archives
AWS_REGION=us-east-1
```

## Model Configuration

| Provider | Model | Input $/1M | Output $/1M | Recommended For |
|----------|-------|-----------|-------------|----------------|
| DeepSeek | deepseek-chat | $0.14 | $0.28 | Default — best value |
| DeepSeek | deepseek-reasoner | $0.59 | $1.85 | Complex reasoning |
| OpenAI | gpt-4o | $2.50 | $10.00 | Premium quality |
| OpenAI | gpt-4o-mini | $0.15 | $0.60 | Budget option |
| Anthropic | claude-sonnet-4 | $3.00 | $15.00 | Long context |
